                            <comment id="84599" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 21 May 2014 15:56:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry I misread the ticket. I was under the impression that the code for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3497&quot; title=&quot;Lustre build system hardcoded to using ZFS development headers in /usr/include only. &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3497&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3497&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; some how got removed by accident. Sorry I haven&apos;t looked into the details. My bad.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="84597" author="brian" created="Wed, 21 May 2014 15:43:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=simmonsja&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;simmonsja&quot;&gt;simmonsja&lt;/a&gt;: No, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5091&quot; title=&quot;LU-4606 breaks --with-zfs-devel option&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5091&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5091&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is about linking the library.  I know, because I opened it.  &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;  The work for using &lt;tt&gt;--with-zfs-devel&lt;/tt&gt; to find the headers is already landed a while ago in  &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3497&quot; title=&quot;Lustre build system hardcoded to using ZFS development headers in /usr/include only. &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3497&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3497&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="84591" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 21 May 2014 15:25:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5091&quot; title=&quot;LU-4606 breaks --with-zfs-devel option&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5091&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5091&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is for headers and this is for linking the library. Yes they could be combined into one patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="84590" author="brian" created="Wed, 21 May 2014 15:23:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is this a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5091&quot; title=&quot;LU-4606 breaks --with-zfs-devel option&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5091&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5091&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?  It seems so but I don&apos;t want to just assume.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
